Package: ScType
Type: Package
Title: Fully-Automated and Ultra-Fast Cell-Type Identification
Version: 2.0.0
Date: 2025-11-18
Authors@R: c(
    person("Aleksandr", "Ianevski", email = "aleksandr.ianevski@helsinki.fi",
           role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Claude", "AI", role = "ctb", comment = "Package structure improvements")
    )
Description: ScType provides fully-automated and ultra-fast cell-type identification
    using specific marker combinations from single-cell transcriptomic data (scRNA-seq).
    The package supports both Seurat and SingleCellExperiment objects, offers hierarchical
    annotation, uncertainty scoring, marker visualization, and pathway enrichment integration.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/IanevskiAleksandr/sc-type, http://sctype.app
